channel.description: DanubScape client has been a very great source/server to start on, unfortuneitly, they have made there own little signatures on the client, the login screen instead of saying "Runescape" now has a picture of 4 differenlt logos say DaNubScape, same with the Inventory in the game, it says, Danub & K0 Kingz own server. Now, Can someone please tell me how to change it to my own picture, and get rid of theres?
